SHG Installation
****************

Prerequisites
-------------

Development environment is Linux debian 6.1.0-13-amd64 (Debian
Bookworm 12.2). For the list of compilers and required libraries, see
make.inc. For Windows, Visual Studio 2019 and 2022 solutions are
provided.

Compilation and testing
-----------------------

Change directory to the main directory of the project. To build the
library, say make lib. To compile the testing program, say make tests.
To run the tests, say make run.

Documentation
-------------

To generate documentation, say make doc. The HTML documentation is
generated in doc/html directory.

Installation
------------

To install the library in /usr/local, say make install. To change the
installation directory, change the prefix variable near the top of
Makefile.
